title: ELEMENT "AUSTIN" MAKE IT COUNT - 2012 INTERNATIONAL SKATE CONTEST SERIES
description:
Jonathan Bastian was the overall winner of the 2012 MAKE IT COUNT Contest in Austin, TX. Jonathan will join other contest winners from all over the world at the finals at Element YMCA Camp in August, along with a trip to The Berrics. The next MAKE IT COUNT Contest will be in Salt Lake City on May 19th.

OVERALL WINNER
Jonathan Bastian

ZONE 1
13 & under - Mason Flynt
14 & up/sponsored - Jonathan Bastian

ZONE 2
13 & under - Aspen McKellop
14 & up/sponsored - Mikey Whitehouse

Music by:
Loren Humphrey
"Six and the City"
